high_descs: Forward toward the shelves, then turn right and move forward, then turn right to face the kitchen island.
Pick up the potato on the kitchen island.
Turn left and go toward the sink, then turn right and go forward, then turn left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the potato inside and chill it, then take the potato out.
Go to the trash bin, to the right of the fridge.
Put the potato in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold potato in the trash bin.

high_descs: Walk across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the end of the kitchen island.
Pick up the closest potato off of the island.
Walk over to the white fridge on your left.
Open the fridge and put the potato inside on the top shelf then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the now chilled potato then close the door.
Turn right and walk over to the wall, then turn left and walk up to the small black bin in the corner of the room.
Put the chilled potato in the small black bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled potato in a small black bin.

high_descs: Take a right at the rack of wooden shelves and walk to the side of the island counter on the right.
Pick up the potato in front of the tea kettle on the counter.
Hang a left at the sink and walk to the white fridge on the left.
Put the potato inside the fridge on the top shelf, chill it, remove it and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the black bin on the floor to the left.
Put the chilled potato inside the black bin on the floor.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled potato in a bin.
